      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapists won't fix the numbers. they can't pay back the investors or erase what happened. it just feels like no matter what i do, the shame is always going to be there. it's just a permanent stain on everything. i feel like i'm just drowning and the more i struggle, the faster i sink. it would be so much easier if everything just... stopped. if i just didn't have to deal with the weight of this anymore.",
